---------------------------------------------------------------------------
                        Welcome to the Fighter Guild!
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
To learn more about a subject, use "fhelp <subject/skill>":

"commands" : This shows general Fighter commands available to you.
             These are typically non-combat commands, but are quite useful
             to you during your career as a Fighter.

"extras"   : This screen shows you extra little "goodies" about Fighters.
             Such as directions to your guild halls on the other
             continents and any other useful insights.

"emote"    : This will show all the Fighter guild emotes.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
